E1J1AUD.original: ~z~Okay it's been a little while since you and me been on a prank like this together,
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~好吧，我俩确实很久没这样一起恶作剧过了，

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~Too bad about those bikes, man. We missed out on a payday.
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~车子的事可惜了，兄弟。这下赚不到钱了。

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~Yeah? Having an old lady and kid hasn't made you scared of getting dirty?
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~是吗？家里有老婆有孩子你还敢这么潇洒？

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~Okay, let's get this truck back to your guy.
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~好了，把这卡车还给你的买家吧。

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~Jackie and the baby, yeah it's nice and all. And shit, I mean I love them and stuff,
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~Jackie和孩子，这样是不错。我是说，我确实很爱他们，

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~It would take a real dumb civilian to screw with our bikes on club turf.
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~再傻逼的人都不会在我们的地盘偷车。

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~You been seeing much of Terry and Clay?
~z~These bikes are over by the Deadbeat hangout in Tudor.
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~这些摩托在死妈天使的Tudor据点附近。

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~And now you're gonna fucking pay us.
~z~I guess you gotta tell your contact he ain't getting those bikes and his truck is screwed.
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~我想你该跟买家说一声他拿不到摩托了，而且他的卡车也毁了。

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~Well, you ain't gonna like what I'm about to do in the next few hours.
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~接下来我准备做的事你可能不大喜欢。

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~You'd think the Deadbeats would know when they were beat.
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~这些死妈天使妈死了都不会懂事啊。

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~You must be really attached to this bike.
~z~It's time to stick it to 'em, Johnny.
~z~You haven't brought them to the house in a while.
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~你有段时间没带他们来会所了。

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~Yeah, man. Fuck all that Billy shit. Let's go.
~z~Just like your daddy paid your momma for sex.
~z~We're cool, Johnny. The AOD won't come this far into Lost territory.
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~我们安全了，Johnny。死亡天使不会贸然踏入失落帮的地盘的。

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~They just don't know when to quit, do they?
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~他们真是不懂得放弃啊，不是吗？

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~Now, you know only a Chapter Head like Billy can ask for that kind of help. So don't go telling him we're coming to ya.
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~先说好，你也知道只有Billy这样的分会会长才能呼叫武力支援。别告诉他我们来帮你了。

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~They got these bikes at their place near Honkers. Drive us, will ya?
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~他们把摩托停在Honkers俱乐部旁边的据点。你开车，好吗？

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~Fuck him, man. He'll deal with it. Later on, Bro.
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~去他妈的，兄弟。他会处理的。回见，兄弟。

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~Don't you fucks know when to give up?
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~你们这些傻逼难道不懂什么时候该放弃吗？

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~Ah, looks like these mopes have outsmarted us, don't it?
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~啊，这俩苦瓜脸好像比我们都聪明了啊？

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~Shit. That guy knows more about tuning a bike than the rest of the brothers put together,
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~靠。那家伙比其他兄弟加起来都懂摩托车，

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~Hey, I hear ya man. But these bikes are the real deal.
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~是啊，我也明白。但这批摩托是真家伙。

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~These assholes don't have the balls to follow us to the clubhouse. We're in the clear, man.
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~这些傻逼不敢跟着我们去会所。我们安全了，兄弟。

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~If it ain't one load of bullshit, it's a God damn n'other.
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~不是这里一团糟，就是那里一团糟。

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~I'm going to go back to the club house, see who's around.
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~我打算回会所了，看看有谁在那。

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~Your parents must have been fuckin' brilliant siblings.
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~你们的双亲肯定是一对天才兄妹。

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~The bikes are parked up by the Tudor Chapter's HQ.
~z~Would somebody tell the Deadbeats that possession is nine tenths of the law.
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~死妈天使都不知道占有人在诉讼中有优势吗。

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~Hey man, Jackie can handle herself but it ain't exactly a family friendly environment at the moment, is it?
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~我说，Jackie能照顾好自己，但现在的会所不适合带家人来，懂吧？

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~Screw it, my brother. Money's just another thing to worry about. See ya, Johnny boy.
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~算了吧，好兄弟。担心钱又是另一回事了。再见，Johnny仔。

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~I guess I'm the thinking type of maniac.
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~我大概是那种思考型的疯子。

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~I was riding bikes before your momma rode your daddy, Jonathan.
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~你妈还在骑你爸的时候我就在骑摩托车了，Jonathan。

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~A guy Angus knows. They met at one of those bike shows.
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~Angus认识的人。他们在车展上认识的。

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~Fucking pricks like those ones made me join The Lost in the first place.
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~就是因为有这种混蛋，我才会加入失落帮。

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~Absolutely. Got to keep active, brother. Keep on moving.
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~当然了。还是要保持心态，兄弟。继续前进吧。

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~You're persistent motherfuckers, I'll give you that.
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~你们这些混蛋很固执啊，不得不承认。

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~Come on, these bikes are ours now.
~z~Hey man, get your asses over here now. Jim and I are in the shit!
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~喂，老兄，快他妈过来。Jim和我遇到麻烦了！

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~These inbred biker rednecks get smarter every year.
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~这些近亲繁殖的红脖子骑手一年比一年聪明。

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~but he's the one who can't ride one no more.
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~只可惜他再也骑不上摩托了。

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~That's right we saw the whole thing you fucking jerk-offs.
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~没错，我们看得一清二楚，两个傻逼。

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~Very funny, asshole. This shit belongs to my contact.
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~好好笑哦，傻逼。这玩意是那个买家的。

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~Get the brothers on the wire, Johnny. We need us some help if we're gonna get home.
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~打电话叫些弟兄来，Johnny。这次想活着回去必须叫点支援。

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~I'm point on this run, let's go.
~z~Jonathan, whatever can I do for you?
~z~but I'm still a brother. Lost MC, man, forever.
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~但我仍然是兄弟。永远都是失落帮的人。

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~turn the cameras off and interrogate her real hard?
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~严刑拷打一顿，看你还觉不觉得自己聪明。

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~Ain't we a little too old for stealing bikes and clubhouse flags and crap like that?
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~我们都多大了，还干这种偷鸡摸狗的勾当啊？

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~Now I got a guy who pays me for them
~z~Fucking Deadbeats. Don't know when to leave good enough alone.
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~傻逼死妈天使。都不知道适可而止的。

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~How smart you gonna feel when we drag your old lady downtown,
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~到时候我们把你老婆抓起来关黑屋子，

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~No one will fuck with our bikes on Lost MC turf.
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~没人敢在失落帮的地盘上对我们的摩托下手。

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~Tommy, they're trying to take your bike.
~z~This is getting too hot, my brother. Why don't you call the boys in to help.
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~事情变得棘手了，兄弟。快打电话叫些支援吧。

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~Can you help a brother in need, Johnny?
~z~She'll be begging us for another fucking interrogation in no fucking time.
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~不用多久她就会哭着求我们再拷问她一次的。

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~Keep the shiny side up and stick behind me, brother.
~z~Call the boys man, they're closing in on us here.
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~找几个弟兄来，敌人逼近我们了。

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~Looks to me like a couple of mopes with some stolen bikes.
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~我看好像是两个苦瓜脸跟几辆赃车。

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~I'm gonna go back to the clubhouse see who's around. Later man.
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~我打算回会所看看有谁在那。回见，兄弟。

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~The brothers are on their way, man.
~z~Feels good to be doing something like this. Not just breaking heads 'cause Billy feels like it.
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~做这种事的感觉真好。比起因为Billy一时兴起就打得头破血流好多了。

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~for some time or, or maybe not ever...?
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~分离一段时间，甚至永远分离...？

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~we're gonna be watching so you better behave yourselves boys.
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~我们就盯着你们，所以你们最好老实点。

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~We got all we can carry, Johnny boy. You and me gotta get outta here.
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~再多也装不下了，Johnny仔。我们得走了。

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~then he ships them over to Japan.
~z~Fucking pricks like those are what made me join The Lost in the first place.
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~就是因为有这种混蛋，我才会加入失落帮。

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~Get your hands off our bike, Loser.
~z~Terry and Clay are coming down, Jim.
~z~It ain't as fast as your bike, but this is our ride, Johnny boy.
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~卡车是没你的摩托快，但就是这次的坐骑，Johnny仔。

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~Johnny, man. I thought you'd lost my number.
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~Johnny，兄弟。我还以为你没有我的号码了。

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~Oh! We've been watching the Angels of Death shitbirds.
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~噢！我们盯了那帮废物死亡天使很久了。

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~So if Billy asked you to do something that meant you wouldn't be able to look after them
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~那万一Billy给你的活会让你跟家人分离，

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~Clay, dude, Me and Jim need some assistance with the AOD.
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~Clay，老兄，我和Jim需要对付死亡天使的帮手。

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~Alright, that's the all of them. Let's get outta here.
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~好了，就这些了。我们离开这儿吧。

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~I always get a kick outta sticking it to them pansies.
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~找那些娘娘腔的麻烦还是那么快乐。

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~Don't you want to come on to Lost turf, assholes?
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~你们敢来失落摩托帮的地盘吗，傻逼？

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~I'm coming close to really losing my shit here.
~z~Skank bitch wouldn't even give her own brother a freebie.
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~连亲兄弟都要收钱的臭婊子。

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~Scared of the brothers, you fucking pussies?
~z~Where'd you get the van, Jim? You ain't turned into some kind of trailer queen have you?
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~这车哪弄来的，Jim？你该不会变成拖车女王*了吧？~n~(指买车不骑，只会装在拖车上炫耀爱车的人)

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~Not really, at least not since Billy got back. Shit's been too crazy.
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~没有，Billy回来后就没怎么聊了。屁事太多了。

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~We taking this truck back to your contact?
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~该把卡车还给你的买家了吧？

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~It's too bad, my brother. I was looking forward to screwing with those Deadbeats.
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~太糟了，好兄弟。我本来想干这群死妈天使一炮的。

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~We should unload a couple of these bikes. A prospect can handle the truck.
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~我们得把摩托卸下来。卡车交给新人处理。

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~Well, you could save me and Jim's hides from some angry Deadbeats. We need your help.
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~你可以从暴怒的死妈天使手里保护我和Jim。我们需要你的帮助。

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~Man, we're only meant to stand up on the Chapter leader's say so, but who gives a fuck? We'll be there.
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~兄弟，原则上只有会长才能叫我们支援，不过去他妈的。我们马上就到。

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~Come to the House if you want a real fight, pussies!
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~有种来我们的地盘干架啊，杂碎们！

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~Apparently they're gonna go crazy for these bikes in particular.
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~那边的人似乎很喜欢这种摩托。

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~Get the bikes, Johnny. I'll scan the horizon.
~z~We got what we came for, brother. Let's move out.
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~车子都到手了，兄弟。我们走吧。

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~Come on, man. Get in the truck.
~z~Them sirens get real tiresome after a while.
~z~Too bad times weren't always this easy...
~z~You should call them, man. They're still cool. Their heads are probably in the same kind of place as yours.
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~多联系他们吧，兄弟。他俩还是你哥们儿，估计想法也跟你差不多。

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~And it better be a big one and while you're at it,
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~最好开个好价。你们一边考虑，

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~But I think long and hard about what I'm gonna order at Burger Shot as well,
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~不过我去汉堡店点餐的时候也需要深思熟虑。

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~If I wanted to take a bike of mine somewhere, I'd drive it myself.
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~要是想出门遛车的话，我会自己骑的。

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~Yeah Johnny, I take your point. I'd have to think long and hard on it, okay?
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~确实，Johnny，我懂你意思。这种情况我就需要深思熟虑了，好吧？

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~This is what The Lost MC is about, Jim. Hell yeah.
~z~Hey, Johnny boy. You know the deal.
~z~We gotta go steal some bikes from the Angels of Death.
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~我们要去偷死亡天使的摩托。

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~Or standing round kicking tires and asking what the fucks gone wrong with the chapter.
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~也好过他问东问西咆哮分会出了问题。

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~Good to be riding just you and me, Jim.
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~只有你和我骑车的感觉真好，Jim。

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~Nobody's gonna be reporting these bikes stolen, so give us a break.
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~没人会来报案找这些车的，放我们一马吧。

E1J1AUD.original: ~z~Luck's a perverse thing ain't it? How are Jackie and the kid?
E1J1AUD.translated: ~z~运气就是这么反复无常啊。Jackie和孩子最近好吗？
